00:29:13,105 --> 00:29:16,486
And we're trying to keep Team Gotham afloat, the company.

557
00:29:17,146 --> 00:29:21,347
But I'm not really sure if it's even worth it anymore.

558
00:29:22,088 --> 00:29:24,029
So I'm not sure if I'm surviving failure,

