00:46:35,226 --> 00:46:37,547
You guys are welcome to approach the various mics.

941
00:46:38,267 --> 00:46:39,968
And either we'll approach the podium

942
00:46:39,988 --> 00:46:40,849
or these mics will turn on.

943
00:46:40,909 --> 00:46:41,529
Or we'll figure it out.

944
00:46:41,569 --> 00:46:41,969
It'll be great.

945
00:46:44,851 --> 00:46:46,131
Just make sure when you ask your question,

946
00:46:46,792 --> 00:46:48,753
say the name of whomever it is you're asking it to,

947
00:46:49,914 --> 00:46:50,554
John, Juan, and Charlie.

948
00:46:54,612 --> 00:46:55,813
if anyone approaches the mic.

949
00:46:55,833 --> 00:47:01,057
Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah.

950
00:47:01,998 --> 00:47:02,919
Let me guess if there's not a...

951
00:47:02,999 --> 00:47:03,579
Yeah, exactly.

952
00:47:06,121 --> 00:47:06,301
Cool.

953
00:47:06,542 --> 00:47:06,902
Hey, John.

